parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Unexpected transmission shifts can cause sudden acceleration or deceleration, leading to loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries.
symptoms: The transmission shifts abruptly into park or another gear
the vehicle accelerates or decelerates suddenly
the vehicle jerks or lurches
the shift lever displays incorrect gear selection
and the parking brake indicator illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission jerking or hard shifting can cause loss of control, accidents, and potential injuries, especially at low speeds.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or lurches when accelerating
the transmission shifts harshly
the brakes grind when applied
and the check engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Transmission Failure to Engage or Disengage
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Transmission failure to engage or disengage can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or strandings.
symptoms: The vehicle fails to shift into gear
the transmission slips or hesitates
the vehicle stalls or loses power
and the check engine light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical charging system can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Low voltage battery light stays illuminated
message "Service Electrical Charging System" and "Low Voltage Vehicle Ma Stall" appears on the message center
low voltage warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the alternator can cause the vehicle to stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Low voltage warning light illuminates
messages "Service Electrical Charging System" and "Low Voltage Vehicle Ma Stall" appear on the message center
alternator produces low voltage (e.g.
8.6 volts).

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the electrical system can cause unintended activation of hazard lights, horn, and tire sensor warning light, leading to accidents or distractions.
symptoms: Hazard lights inadvertently illuminate
horn inadvertently honks
tire sensor warning light illuminates.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear liftgate locking mechanism can cause cargo to exit the vehicle, leading to accidents or damage.
symptoms: Rear liftgate does not latch
cargo exits the vehicle
no warning is given when the rear liftgate is open and unlatched.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the infotainment system can cause the rear-facing camera image to not display, leading to reduced visibility and potential accidents.
symptoms: Infotainment screen appears black
red triangle and circle with a line through it appear on the screen.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of OnStar and WiFi connectivity can cause inconvenience and reduce the functionality of the vehicle's systems.
symptoms: OnStar system and WiFi intermittently do not work
even when radio is not being used.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seat/mirror position memory can cause inconvenience and reduce the comfort of the vehicle's occupants.
symptoms: Seat/mirror position memory gradually changes over time
does not recognize that exit function has been turned off.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tire pressure monitoring system can cause inaccurate readings, leading to reduced safety and potential accidents.
symptoms: Tire pressure monitoring system notifies driver of underpressured tires by 10lb or more
inaccurate readings.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The grinding noise of the brakes can cause reduced safety and potential accidents.
symptoms: Brakes on passenger front randomly grind
dealership indicates obvious electrical issue but cannot repair due to lack of codes.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water leaking from the sunroof can cause damage to the vehicle's interior, electrical systems, and potentially lead to accidents due to distraction or obstruction of the driver's view.
symptoms: Water pouring into the driver's seat from the ceiling
water leaking into the vehicle's interior
sunroof glass shattering or exploding without apparent cause.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the sunshade clip can cause the sunshade to malfunction, obstructing the driver's view and potentially leading to accidents.
symptoms: Rear sunshade clip breaks
sunshade malfunctions
obstruction of driver's view.
